Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:03.15,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:05.82,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm a famous high school detective known throughout the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.76,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I was forced to take a pill by some organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.43,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}...and became Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:10.50,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.30,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My mind's that of a brilliant 17-year old detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.99,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can solve cases that not even adults can handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.94,Signs,Comment,0,0,0,,Mouri Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:01.21,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's been 3 days since I shrunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:07.32,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}There still hasn't been any information about the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:17.80,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But nobody would ask a detective like him for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}much less give him information about those men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.13,Dialogue Top,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.85,Dialogue Top,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go! Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.75,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on now, you're too old to be acting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.71,Dialogue Top,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko! Yoko! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.77,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}You set the example for hopeless men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.11,Dialogue Top,Comment,0,0,0,,"Teitan Elementary School"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,2 times 2 is 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,2 times 3 is 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,2 times 4 is 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's walk home together, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You must feel kind of lonely since you just transferred here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So we'll be your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, um, I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying no to Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Violence isn't good, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:01.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! You got a problem with me, Mitsuhiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I gotta go, I'm really busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never find those men in black if things keep up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just be patient, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Think what would happen if you rushed things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and they found out that you're really Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:20.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:24.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It would put not just me but all the people around me in real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} came by yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:27.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.51,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi didn't come to school again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.84,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And it doesn't look like he's been home either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.40,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think I'll call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.51,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:38.12,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure he's just working on another one of his strange cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.81,Flashback,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry. He'll be back home soon enough, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:49.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got her convinced for the time being, but how long can we keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.03,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:03.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I made something you'll find useful for your cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a Voice-Altering Bow Tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,"Voice-Altering"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:13.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Turn the dial on the back and you can make all kinds of voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You can sound like an old man, a child, a man, and even a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm certain it'll come in handy at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:28.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I doubt that a detective agency would have much use for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We have no choice, we're gonna force him to be our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:58.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The Mouri Detective Agency is closed today. If you've got a job for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...come back... tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh my god! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko Okino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No way! What would a celebrity be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:10.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I want to hire you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You appear to be troubled, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Somebody's spying on you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The furniture's been moved whenever I come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,somebody's been sending me candid photos they took of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and I've been getting anonymous phone calls everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare they!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If at all possible, we'd like you to look into it quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:46.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm Yamagishi, her manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Her manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.78,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Very well. I will investigate as discreetly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll need your address and phone number here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:54.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And if you could autograph this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't forget to write "To Kogoro"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that the great detective Kogoro Mouri is on the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,you have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Can I come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see a celebrity's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just don't be getting in the way! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This is exactly the kind of place I thought Yoko Okino might live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Nobody's supposed to know she lives here, it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The 25th floor, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} in the flesh... awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We definitely have to make friends with Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.01,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:20.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So he had already been murdered by the time you got back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:24.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And the person with you at the time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...was me, Kogoro Mouri, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.48,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why {\i1}him{\i0}, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just like old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember all those cases we worked on together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:40.38,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. And thanks to you most of them went unsolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It certainly is hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you always have the heater on this high?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'm sure I turned it off before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That isn't the only thing that's odd, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:08:00.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,They're very faint, but there are damp spots all around the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.38,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And this chair is the only thing still standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,while everything else in the room has been thrown about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And this heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Was it done to disguise the time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Kids shouldn't get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That means you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you determined the cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It would seem this knife was the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that knife belong to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't honestly suspect Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you seen the victim before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, I'd have to take a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So have you seen him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I guess we haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:45.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure I saw him—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.76,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that? What did he pick up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.81,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}A strand of hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.42,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would her manager try to hide this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.32,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could the murderer have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The murder took place while the door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:21.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means the murderer was the apartment's resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No! I could never kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She's telling the truth, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just because she has a key doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't people usually have a spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!{double up}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey now, stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, Yamagishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has my spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:40.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamagishi! You're the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:44.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko gave you the cold shoulder so you took it out on him, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:47.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, now. Where's the proof that she didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:52.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful young woman would never do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.19,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I did have her spare key, but I lost it 2 or 3 days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.63,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I was in the dressing room at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I can vouch for him, he told me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, if that's what Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.48,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get the feeling that we're still lacking something really important
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.17,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}that could explain everything here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,An earring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector, under that sofa—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:26.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You kids stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.98,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dang it, they all ignore me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! This thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll just set it to an adult's voice, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:38.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Inspector, there's something beneath the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,An earring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Yuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuko Ikezawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.\NShe debuted the same time I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:55.22,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that she was upset that Yoko got her role in a drama series...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.19,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:01.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The murderer was Yuko Ikezawa!\NArrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:02.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll have to go to the station—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.63,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, let's have her come here for questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You heard the inspector! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:10.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:15.13,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yuko Ikezawa did it!\NThere's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:19.67,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Judging from the scene of the crime, the murderer must be Yoko Okino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.71,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The manager's inexplicable action...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.91,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the odd marks left behind in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.19,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}All the pieces are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.42,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The question is how to put them together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The murder took place in Yoko's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She's the one you should suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:54.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never been here before now. I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what was this doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:01.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I lost that somewhere! I'm glad you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't stop with the earring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:07.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The superintendent also said that he's seen someone who looks like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone who looks like me? This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing your bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You never give up, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You think I'm the murderer just because of an earring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm really busy, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:25.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Not nearly as busy as little Miss Popular Celebrity, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But if the media gets wind of this your image'll take a nosedive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll lose as much work as I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.78,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you threaten her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:45.23,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}They both look exactly the same from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:48.70,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And how did she know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, grownups!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way of their investigation, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:04.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But if Shin'ichi were here he'd easily solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:09.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where could that mystery geek have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry! He'll be back, I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I mean, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What do I have to say for you to understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I already told you I've never been here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a pretty weird lighter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:34.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How did you know this was a lighter if you've never been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. Care to explain how you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I know someone who has one just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And where does this someone live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.19,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never been here before so I don't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Eh? It's in the hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:54.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you knew where the bathroom was too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Which is because you, Yuko Ikezawa, are the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:03.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You killed that man in this apartment to create a big scandal around Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,All I did was defend myself when he suddenly attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll admit it, I did sneak in here several times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:16.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,using the spare key I stole from the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:19.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to find something, anything, that could cause a scandal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:24.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But when I came in this afternoon, that man suddenly showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I defended myself with all of my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...and then escaped as quickly as I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:35.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't really kill him in the heat of the moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I said I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:41.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We've learned the identity of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Akiyoshi Fujie, 22 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.38,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Upon graduating from Konan High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,he began working for Kakubeni Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Konan High School...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that your old high school, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:59.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:04.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I didn't just know him, he was my high school boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:11.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamagishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. I can't hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:15.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you did this to break up with your old flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:19.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, he was the one who dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.08,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.42,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's the murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.25,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yoko Okino?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yuko Ikezawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.56,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yamagishi, the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.03,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're still missing something we need to make any deductions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.83,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it? What are we missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.17,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}A dent in the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.40,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.51,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even though the room's in shambles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.41,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}this chair is the only thing left standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.97,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}And this room's exceptionally high temperature...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:53.01,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The water splotches left around the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.44,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hair in the corpse's hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}A-ha! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've finally solved the puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.63,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...is you, Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You saw him as an obstacle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,because he was capable of starting a scandal around Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you ran into him while he was hiding in here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and proceeded to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.14,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.80,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yamagishi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} isn't the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What a nice nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're conscious again, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the only one left who could be the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.99,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Forgive me, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Fess up! You'll feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:49.34,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now then, I'll just set it to his voice, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Which is what I would like to say, but that isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamagishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If you really asked me to help you so that I would discover the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,you would have also prepared something to prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the same goes for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:07.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,especially since the 1st person to suspect would be the apartment's tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:11.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So then the murderer...\Nis Yuko Ikezawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She didn't do it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if she did commit the murder in the heat of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,she wouldn't have told us she ran into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But what you're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, these are only educated guesses at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:26.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,They don't hold up as proof that the three of them are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But there is evidence to support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamagishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:33.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You pretended to slip and then removed strands of hair from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it! I knew you were the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The man was stabbed in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but he was holding the stabber's hair in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you find that a bit odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The one responsible set it all up to look like a murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:54.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,As if he was killed by Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,"Like a murder"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The killer is none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...the late Fujie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:11.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Nonsense! How could he stab himself in the back with a knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a simple trick involving ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:19.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He set the heater on high, took hairs from Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s brush,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:23.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,then stood up on a chair and fell back onto a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,that was held in place by a block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:29.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll find the indentation mark made by the knife's handle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,near where the body was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:34.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The ice shattered and later melted because of the high heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:38.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,However, Fujie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} tried too hard to frame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,When Yamagishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:47.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,he tried to hide it because he thought Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had indeed killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But why would Fujie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:54.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I would think that it was because he still loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:19:00.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you realize that the two of you look exactly the same from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:04.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So he mistook Yuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and attacked—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No. He tried to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:10.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Not realizing he was talking to Yuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and not Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,he was completely shocked when she resisted him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:17.62,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and the feelings of his love being driven to the wall turned into despair and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:20.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But he dumped me! Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, that's not the truth, Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:27.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The truth is, I asked him to break up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:30.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We've found a diary in the late Fujie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:42.14,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The diary was filled with his pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:43.31,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}How even after they broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.08,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}he was unable to forget about her, so he went to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:51.22,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}He hoped she would end her career as a celebrity and come back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.56,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}All he wanted to do was clear up the misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:58.49,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The last thing he wrote was that he couldn't live like this any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:05.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It would appear this was a tragic story that consisted of lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,misunderstandings, and coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:16.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind about you,\N"Great Detective"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a little scary, but I've never been that excited before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I think if we make friends with Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,we'll get to experience lots more thrills and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright then! We've gotta get Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to be our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.01,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,She's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Already back on her feet after all that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:07.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I could never do that.\NI could never be as strong as Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:11.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep at night with Shin'ichi gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm really hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:54.54,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:57.87,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi has been missing for a week now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.48,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something must have happened to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:03.68,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}But nothing like that would ever happen to Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:07.77,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi... Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello, Mouri Detective—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:16.88,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:18.42,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:20.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:25.33,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I figured you might be crying because you're worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:29.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. Why would I be crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:32.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you right now, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I was asked to take a sort of dangerous case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll come back home once I've taken care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:39.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:42.85,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:48.36,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I return to my normal body, I'll let you hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My real voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:52.69,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My real feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:09.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:09.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,60 seconds until the next episode's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:05.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think these drawings could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:08.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's a treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:11.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's time for some treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.31,0:24:14.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,From this day forth we'll be known as the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:18.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna use that treasure\Nto eat the world's best eel dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:19.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.99,0:24:21.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll save it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:27.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.42,0:24:33.42,Dialogue Top,Comment,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.42,0:24:38.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Neon Sign
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.49,0:24:41.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, can you crack the code?
